            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Trees of the $(thing)Misty World$() are less straight-forward to cultivate than most. Of particular note, is the way saplings are harvested from the trees. This is done by $(l)breaking $(item)Branches$() $(l)at their thinnest point, where they attach to the $(item)Leaves$(). The more $(item)Leaves$() attached to the branch, the more likely you will successfully prune a $(item)Sapling$()."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Growing Seeds",
            "text": "The other way to obtain $(item)Saplings$() is by growing $(item)Tree Seeds$(), plucked from the leaves during specific $(l:dimension_dossier/misty_world/seasons)Seasons$(). Once you've got a seed, plant it in a $(item)Flower Pot$() and given a little time it'll grow up into a $(item)Sapling$()."
        },
